      "message": "I think my original plan is to make RM not consuming the events. But as this kind of scenario is rare, so I decide to take on this easier but not-so-efficient approach. Now, since OnCLUpdated also requires this, I think I will implement your #1 approach which is also my original plan. Leaving a TODO.",
